msgctxt "talk132"
msgid ""
"<1.so>The north?<2.pa> Oh, right...<3.pa>\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"<4.so>On the other side of Mount Rhoam,\n"
"there's an odd lad named <5.se_co>Konba<6.re_co> who\n"
"loves challenging strangers to a race.\n"
"He must be REALLY bored. It might be\n"
"nice of you to pay him a visit."
msgstr ""

